self.ML.eventname = None
loc = get_file_path('custom_data2.csv')
self.ML.Load_Data(loc=loc, dataset_type='custom', filter_outlier_percent=10)
self.assertTrue(self.ML.data.shape == (8, 3))
self.ML.Clear_Data()
self.ML.Load_Data(loc=loc, dataset_type='custom', filter_outlier_percent=(0,
    90))
self.assertTrue(self.ML.data.shape == (9, 3))
self.ML.Clear_Data()
self.ML.Load_Data(loc=loc, dataset_type='custom', filter_outlier_percent=0.1)
self.assertTrue(self.ML.data.shape == (8, 3))
self.ML.Clear_Data()
self.ML.Load_Data(loc=loc, dataset_type='custom', filter_outlier_percent=0.2)
self.assertTrue(self.ML.data.shape == (6, 3))
self.ML.Clear_Data()
